name: Query
extra-info: SELECT 100.00 * sum( CASE WHEN p_type LIKE 'PROMO%' THEN l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) ELSE 0 END) / sum(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS promo_revenue FROM lineitem, part WHERE l_partkey = p_partkey AND l_shipdate >= date '1995-09-01' AND l_shipdate < CAST('1995-10-01' AS date);
